<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>10287</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>21615</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>从前，有一个聪明的男孩儿。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>21615</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>30364</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他的名字叫杰克。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>30364</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>34270</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>杰克和他的妈妈一起生活。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>34270</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>39026</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们很穷。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>39026</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>46857</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>很久以前，一个邪恶的食人魔偷走了他们的金子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>46857</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>53407</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>后来，杰克的爸爸去世了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>53407</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>60093</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>现在他们只有一个菜园和一块麦田。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>60093</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>66816</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>还有一头名字叫米可的老奶牛。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>66816</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>70862</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>杰克每天早上去挤牛奶。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>70862</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>74803</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后他下午去市场。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>74803</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>83883</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“牛奶！新鲜的牛奶！” 杰克大喊，“还有新鲜的黄油！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>83883</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>95167</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>晚上回到家，杰克把钱给妈妈。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>95167</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>103459</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>有一年，下了很大的暴风雨。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>103459</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>107411</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>雨水冲毁了他们的菜园。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>107411</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>110297</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>也冲毁了他们的麦田。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>110298</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>113959</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>妈妈看了看四周，摇了摇头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>113959</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>122167</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她说：“我们该怎么办？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>122167</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>127827</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“别担心，妈妈！” 杰克温柔地说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>127827</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>131342</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“春天我们可以建一个新的花园！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>131342</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>135527</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>可以种更多的小麦！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>135527</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>138676</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>而且我们还有米可！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>138676</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>143842</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>妈妈点了点头：“你说得对，杰克。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>143842</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>147886</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我们还有米可！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>147886</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>152025</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>有一天，杰克去挤牛奶。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>152025</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>156719</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他挤了挤，但是没有牛奶。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>156719</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>163269</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“希望米可没事。” 杰克心想。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>163269</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>168088</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>第二天，杰克又去挤牛奶。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>168088</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>172834</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哦，不！” 他说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>172834</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>177203</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>真的没有牛奶了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>177203</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>187711</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>杰克叹了口气：“我该怎么告诉妈妈呢？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>